column3:
Softknox has told you about Rival Wings, a new type of war game incorporating goblin-made machina. If the thought of such fighty-play gives you heartthumps, you can learn more from Softknox...or dive straight into the action.

※Astragalos can be accessed via the Duty Finder.

Pshhh... Shkohhh...
Softknox comes to wolf place, learns that uplanders have many heartthumps for fighty-play.
Softknox sees chance for busydeal. Offers gobbie hand-lending for uplanders to have <Emphasis>better</Emphasis> fighty-play. Crunch bone and smash steel muchly!
Now new fighty-play is born, name of “Rival Wings”! Machina of gobmake help uplanders make much mayhem together!
If uplander wishes to fill braincase with knowings of Rival Wings, Softknox happy to give many tongueflaps!
Pshhh... Shkohhh... Gobbies make new fighty-play to give many heartthumps. Does uplander have strong enough bladder to try?
In order to undertake this quest, you must meet the following requirements:
※ You must be at least level 30 with a Disciple of War or Magic.
※ You must be affiliated with a Grand Company and have unlocked the Feast.
